sentences.sentence: This time, only five embryos were needed to produce each one of the Dollies.
sentences.translation: 这一次，制造多莉只用了五个胚胎。

sentences.sentence: Raise rear of vehicle off ground and install tow dollies under rear wheels.
sentences.translation: 将车辆后侧举离地面，在后轮下安装拖曳支架。

sentences.sentence: Raise the front of the vehicle off the ground and install tow dollies under front wheels.
sentences.translation: 将车辆前方举起离地，在前轮下安装两个拖曳支架。
